name: Wokling (V)
Lore: 'Every Ewok is taught to be protective of the younger members of their clan.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Your total Force generation is +1.  Once per game, may use 3 Force to take an Effect that has no deploy cost and deploys on another card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  May place this Effect out of play to retrieve 1 Force. (Immune to Alter.)(Original concept by Eric Hunter - Gen Con Winner 2002)',
